                    <h2 class=" ">Top Tips for studying the P&amp;IQ</h2>
                    <p>
                        
                            This page outlines approaches that helped two P&amp;IQ candidates - Helen Chitten, Senior Claims Manager, and Mayur Sawant, the Group Secretariat.  They share their guidance on time management, revision planning, note taking, and staying focused.
                        
                    </p>
                    <a href="/article/top-tips-for-studying-the-piq/">
                        <img alt="Play button"
