                    <div class="fake-tint-overlay ">
                        <h2 class="mt-0 ">The International Group Pooling and Group Excess of Loss Reinsurance contract (GXL) structure for the 2026/27 Policy Year has now been finalised</h2>
                        <p class="text-white">
                            
                                The International Group (IG) Pooling and Group Excess of Loss Reinsurance contract (GXL) structure for the 2026/27 Policy Year has now been finalised.
                            
                        </p>
                        <a href="/article/the-international-group-pooling-and-group-excess-of-loss-reinsurance-contract-gxl-structure-for-the-202627-policy-year-has-now-been-finalised/">
