                </div>
                <div class="hero-case-study mb-3 mb-lg-0 mt-lg-1 mt-2 col-lg-6">
                    
                        <div class="background-image ig-border-radius bg-ig-blue"></div>
                    
                    <div class="alt-herobar fake-tint-overlay ">
                        <h2 class="mt-0 ">Rolf Thore Roppestad appointed Group Chair of the International Group of P&amp;I Clubs</h2>
                        <p>
                            
                                At the Annual General Meeting of the International Group of P&amp;I Clubs, held in London on 11 November 2025, Rolf Thore Roppestad was appointed as the new Group Chair.
                            
                        </p>
